title: tethercord
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A tethercord is a springlike device with two small packets filled with diluted [[sovereign glue]]. Flinging this trap at an enemy causes one side to stick to the creature, while the other bonds to the ground, keeping the target on a short leash.